column1: + 1 User associate 1 User (User is associated with another User for admin and player roles)
+ 1 User associate 0..* PlayedGame (User plays 0 or more PlayedGames)
+ 1 Game associate 1 Admin (Each Game has exactly 1 Admin)
+ 1 Game associate 1..* Level (Each Game has one or more Levels)
+ 1 Game associate 1 HallOfFameEntry (Each Game has a HallOfFame)
+ 1 Level associate 1..* BlockAssignment (Each Level has one or more BlockAssignments)
+ 1 Level associate 1 PlayedGame (Each Level is associated with one PlayedGame)
+ 1 PlayedGame associate 1..* PlayedBlockAssignment (Each PlayedGame has one or more PlayedBlockAssignments)
+ 1 PlayedGame associate 1 PlayedBall (Each PlayedGame has one PlayedBall)
+ 1 PlayedGame associate 1 PlayedPaddle (Each PlayedGame has one PlayedPaddle)
+ 1 PlayedGame associate 1 Player (Each PlayedGame is associated with one Player)
+ 1 Game contain 1..* Level (Each Game contains one or more Levels)
+ 1 Level contain 1..* BlockAssignment (Each Level contains one or more BlockAssignments)
+ 1 PlayedGame contain 1 PlayedBall (Each PlayedGame contains one PlayedBall)
+ 1 PlayedGame contain 1 PlayedPaddle (Each PlayedGame contains one PlayedPaddle)
+ 1 PlayedGame contain 1..* PlayedBlockAssignment (Each PlayedGame contains one or more PlayedBlockAssignments)
+ User extends Player (User is a type of Player)
+ User extends Admin (User is a type of Admin)
